author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Welcome to Game 4 of out  Studio League Season 2!

Six players will play over the next 5 months to crown one winner!  We keep track of Wins and losses which populate an ever changing leaderboard leading to a single elimination tournament at the end. Lets see which player comes out on top!

One twist this season is that while a player is allowed to play any faction they want, they can never play the same detachment twice!  Time to test your skill no matter what.  Lets see who wins the fabled crown of Chadocles!

===============GAME INFO=============
Mitch  tries another detachment of Black Templar in an attempt to claw back a win while Michael comes fresh with a force of Emperor's Children!  This could be a bloody one!

===============ARMY LIST=============

title: Studio League Season 2 - Game 4 - Emerorors' Children vs Black Templar
